93
00:07:19,875 --> 00:07:22,375
<i>T'es à bonne distance, doucement.</i>

94
00:07:22,375 --> 00:07:23,833
Oui, deux secondes.

95
00:07:28,791 --> 00:07:30,375
Putain !
Ça va ?

96
00:07:30,375 --> 00:07:31,750
<i>Ouais, ça va.</i>

97
00:07:31,750 --> 00:07:33,458
- C'est bon, remontez.

98
00:07:33,458 --> 00:07:36,208
