127
00:11:56,250 --> 00:11:57,541
Ouf !

128
00:11:57,541 --> 00:11:59,041
Ça va ?
- Ouais.

129
00:12:00,583 --> 00:12:01,416
C'est quoi ?

130
00:12:17,416 --> 00:12:20,458
La BS est sur place...
