Venez, vite !

902
01:22:57,541 --> 01:22:59,750
Berruti, viens !

903
01:23:11,458 --> 01:23:15,458
Surtout, ne bougez plus.
Il faut absolument rester groupés.

904
01:23:31,500 --> 01:23:32,833
Non, Adama !

905
01:23:42,791 --> 01:23:43,666
Reviens, Adama !

906
01:23:43,666 --> 01:23:45,083
Barrez-vous !

907
