- Sophia ! Adil !

910
01:25:21,666 --> 01:25:24,041
Vite ! Venez !
Nage !

911
01:25:24,041 --> 01:25:25,083
Vite !

912
01:25:35,333 --> 01:25:37,583
Donne-moi ton bras ! Ton bras !

913
01:25:43,875 --> 01:25:45,125
Ça va aller.

914
